/inventors></us-parties><assignees><assignee><addressbook><orgname>QUILTS OF DENMARK A/S</orgname><role>03</role><address><city>Vamdrup</city><country>DK</country></address></addressbook></assignee></assignees></us-bibliographic-data-application><abstract id="abstract"><p id="p-0001" num="0000">The present invention relates to a sleeping device, such as a mattress, quilt or pillow, wherein the sleeping device is adapted to be used by a person during rest and comprises a core element, wherein said core element is covered by a first layer of a material having temperature regulating properties by absorbing and releasing heat and a second layer of down. By using a material with temperature regulating properties together with a layer of down filling, very good properties of minimizing temperature variations are obtained.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>